{"tid":50402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【盲亨女墮海亡】男友話殉情有疑點 當晚有人聽到女子嗌救命","createTime":"2016-12-22T11:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T01:34:10.000Z","uid":22736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92ee984912ff5942f63c871e62bb60c331a434c3","tid":50402,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161222&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56077816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161222%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56077816&d=FWXRXA3W5kmi1UuwQ2ATinvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=50938f66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161222%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D56077816&h=66f86a34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161222&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=56077816</a><br />\n8：30更新】新增動新聞<br />\n【17：30更新】最新消息稱，警方認為詹詠嵐墮海身亡事件有疑點，據知事發當晚在墮海現場附近的屋苑，有住客聽到女子「嗌救命」，隨即報警，惟最後救上來的竟是一名男子，令住客和保安員都嘖嘖稱奇，但事發三小時後，再有人報案指發現海上有人形物體漂浮，可惜水警輪到場搜索後無發現收隊。警方正循有疑點方向調查"},{"pid":"be8b9d25d441b8fdae0b3502f7f262b82a8d9d90","tid":50402,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c869340dbe8197988c0fcc786fb0c1839afe135","tid":50402,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"條仔比老黑收兵？"},{"pid":"7779f1e4f00556771664e691c2593f3c76b29477","tid":50402,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ceb1faf9f254245c6ca94e8993d1f03dc16c532","tid":50402,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:21:14.000Z","msg":"被殉情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4de64eb